<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>ت ف ل<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٩٥٦ - ت ف ل]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>تفَلَ يَتفُل ويَتفِل، تَفْلاً، فهو تافِل، والمفعول متفول <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• تفَلَ الشَّخصُ:</span> تفَّ، بصَق.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• تفَل الماءَ ونحوَه:</span> مجَّه كراهَةً له <span class="c1">"تفَل الدَّواء المُرَّ"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>